{"type":null,"faqId":10932,"title":"荣耀3C （H30-T10&H30-U10）   添加/取消闹钟","answer":"<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span>a)<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">时钟</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。再点击</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31995\" width=\"22\" height=\"20\" />&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入闹钟界面。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31993\" /><br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span>b)<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">选择</span><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31994\" width=\"45\" height=\"35\" /> </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">添加闹钟</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，进入设置闹钟界面，可以进行如下操作：</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span>c)<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击<b>时间</b>，设置闹钟铃响的时间。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span>d)<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击<b>重复</b>，选择需要闹钟重复的周期。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span>e)<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击<b>铃声</b>，选择闹钟铃声。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span>f)<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">勾选<b>振动</b>，设置手机在闹钟铃响时振动。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span>g)<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击<b>标签，</b>输入闹钟时间名称。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-21pt;margin-left:72.05pt;\">\n\t<span>h)<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击<b>完成</b>，完成闹钟的添加。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在闹钟界面，可以看到当前所有闹钟的列表，去掉一条闹钟前面的勾选，就表示取消了这个闹钟。或长按一条闹钟记录，在弹出菜单中选择“<b>删除闹钟</b>”删除您选择的闹钟。</span> \n</p>\n<br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1692","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1397788865000,"seriesProductName":"H30-T10,H30-U10","visitedTimes":193,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀3C （H30-T10&H30-U10）","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}